Charizs Shields Shopping Site

Project Brief

The Charizs Shields Shopping Site is an online platform designed to offer a wide range of protective cases for electronic devices. The website aims to provide a user-friendly and visually appealing shopping experience, with easy navigation and a straightforward checkout process.

Hypotheses

Hypothesis 1: Providing a wide range of product options will increase the likelihood of customer purchases.
Hypothesis 2: A clean and simple website design will enhance user experience and reduce bounce rates.

Features

Main Navigation Bar: Allows users to easily navigate through different sections of the website.
Product Display: Showcases products with high-quality images and detailed descriptions.
Subscription Form: Enables users to subscribe to newsletters for updates and promotions.

Technologies Used
HTML
CSS
JavaScript

Repository Structure
/assets: Contains images and other static files.
/scripts: Contains JavaScript files.
/styles: Contains CSS files.
index.html: Main entry point of the website.
